query:
INSERT INTO agent_wallets (
                id,
                profile_key,
                display_name,
                budget_limit,
                spent_amount
            ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, 0)
            ON CONFLICT(profile_key) DO UPDATE SET
                display_name = excluded.display_name,
                budget_limit = excluded.budget_limit,
                updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
